propertyIndex.description:
Add an index to a property. Examples:

"property_foo": { "type": "String", "index": true },



"email": { "type": "String", "index": {"unique": true} }

acls.description:
The value of the `acls` key is an array of objects that describes the access controls for the model. Example: 

{ "permission": "ALLOW", "principalType": "ROLE", "principalId": "$everyone", "property": "myMethod"}

http://loopback.io/doc/en/lb3/Model-definition-JSON-file#ModeldefinitionJSONfile-ACLs

indexes.description:
Declare indexes for a model 
Example:

 "name_age_index": { "keys": {"name": 1, "age": -1} }

 "age_index": {"age": -1} }

http://loopback.io/doc/en/lb3/Model-definition-JSON-file#ModeldefinitionJSONfile-Indexes
